{"tid":824910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[旅遊界義載] 紅磡 -> 沙田, 觀塘 -> 上水","createTime":"2018-09-17T09:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T10:19:23.000Z","uid":42188,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d454e44fac5cc581b96b5da609646950ddcb413","tid":824910,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/172436_52a9b24214f14e21b6d547d80e919d58.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F172436_52a9b24214f14e21b6d547d80e919d58.png&h=65fda4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬通旅行社董事羅啟邦指，因火車服務嚴重故障，新界東市民出入大受影響，故在今晚放工時間，即傍晚6時至7時期間，動員旅遊巴「義載」居民返新界東，路線包括紅磡站平台（5C巴士站向尖東方向）往沙田新城市廣場；及觀塘APM（巧明街出口）往上水站，客滿即走，先到先得。"},{"pid":"90b61f215b723149ce2491f69f4d4f23e64da69e","tid":824910,"uid":73613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:26:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b451b64cb40488a7de63f626c8bdc7ef13cf7424","tid":824910,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"做人冇公關，食屎啦，三條柒你明唔明呀"},{"pid":"7c011c1761be4649aa653bc21280113806d3c0ad","tid":824910,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b61f215b723149ce2491f69f4d4f23e64da69e","tid":824910,"uid":73613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T09:26:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T10:19:23.000Z","msg":"條友實發達<br />\n出多日糧 少少油錢"}]}